column5: Since we have a new message board  , I decided to update the Official OFC Monopoly board
Okay, do we use house and hotels, or will it be cottages, boats and tackle to get rent when you land on someones place.  This could go somewhere.
DANG, I didn't make it again  I figured for sure I'd get at least Joey's Jail  Looks great kiddo.  Joey
I know how ya feel Joey... still no GCD Gardens for me
Nice work Cory!  Whopper
And no Tracker Trail - Maybe the next remake.   Don
Kemper Trail....  Kemper's Coop...  Kemper's landing....   Kemper's sunked again...
That is awesome!!!
Lookin' nice.  I want one!
BPS BASSMAN BLVD gotta love it!! Do we have to sign the new one again at the next swill Nice head Herc
LOL, thx Roger... I think.
That's creative.

Great job, Cory!  I remember fishing with your Dad this summer, & we were thinking that we should've remembered the first board I still haven't signed...plus, he fished with Lew the next day & he could've signed it too.  Next time, for sure.
Pretty sweet lets put it into production
Very good Jr.  Maureen
Cory, that's kewl  John
Like it, very cool...
I assume this will be available on the OFC Store.  Can't wait - haven't played that game in a lot of years.
I guess ya should have brought the first one to the fishing show maybe we can all sign it this Xmas. Nice job again
I'm still waiting for delivery of my board.  See you guys soon enough maybe we can play a couple rounds by boat teams.
Mike you dug up a good one  You bring the money I'll bring the dice
